{
  "chapter": 142,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲随王世充船队抵达洛阳，沿途听其介绍城内水陆交通之便利与鲁妙子设计的开合桥。王世充以封寇仲为洛阳王为诱饵，诱其交出杨公宝库秘密。与此同时，徐子陵与李靖重逢，得知李靖早已移情别恋娶妻，素素当年正是因此黯然离去，徐子陵愤而与李靖断交。船队抵达皇城外，郎奉已暗中控制洛阳局势。寇仲提醒王世充警惕独孤凤的实力，王世充对独孤阀隐藏实力深感不安。徐子陵独自漫步洛阳城中，偶遇窦建德大将刘黑闼。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇小兄到过洛阳吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "尚是首次到洛阳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们下面这条洛水，把都城一分为二，成南北两部分。皇宫和皇城位于城西北部；街、坊、市均分布在城南和东部。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "船队可直接驶进城内去吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不但可驶进城内，还可抵达任何地方，若论内外水陆交通的便利，天下没有一个城市可及得上东都。除洛水贯穿其中外，还有东河、西谷水、北金水渠、南通津渠、通济渠、伊水、漕渠、道渠、重津渠、丹水渠与大街小巷纵横交错，车船相接方便无此。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若你助我东破李密，西克长安，我便封你为洛阳王，此城就是你的封邑，而小妮妮便是你的王妃！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "多谢圣上龙恩！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人传你两人知道'杨公宝库'的秘密，究竟是真是假？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "我们只有一些线索，能否找到仍是未知之数。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "宝藏究竟是否在洛阳呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "尚书真厉害！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "昔年建设新都时，杨素曾积极参与，要弄个宝藏该是顺理成章的事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要撞桥哩！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这是我们中土第一座开合桥，出自天下巧艺大宗师鲁妙子的设计，寇小兄没有见过并不足怪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那就是皇宫，我们直接去见杨侗，看他能耍出甚么花样来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_li_jing",
      "text": "李大哥成亲了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jing",
      "speaker_name": "李靖",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "已有多年了！当年我和素妹亡命北上，幸好遇上了她，得她义助，接回我一条断筋，否则你的李大哥已变成一个跛子。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jing",
      "speaker_name": "李靖",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵的脸色为何变得这么难看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_li_jing",
      "text": "由今天起，我们再非兄弟，李靖你走吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jing",
      "speaker_name": "李靖",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "究竟是甚么一回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_li_jing",
      "text": "你该清楚知道是甚么一回事，枉素姐对你情深一片，你却移情别恋。我们之间再没有甚么话好说。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_jing",
      "speaker_name": "李靖",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "由于李密不知你和淑妮早已脱身，所以消息该尚未传返洛阳，只看现在杨侗全无防备，恐怕到现在仍未知我王世充已回来了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "这叫以快打慢，只要我们能控制杨侗，独孤阀便失去最大的凭藉，那时要杀要剐，再不由他们决定了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "独孤峰武功虽高，但仍未放在我心上，但那老婆子尤楚红却真是非同小可，我旗下虽高手如云，恐怕仍没有人拦得她住，若给她漏网逃去，会是个很大的祸患。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "为何尚书不提独孤凤呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "为何要提她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "吾友跋锋寒曾和独孤凤交手，差点便不能脱身。据说她的武功已超越了独孤峰，仅次于尤楚红，尚书怎会一无所知的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若真有此事，那说不定独孤阀仍有其他隐藏起来的实力，用以伺机暗算我。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "定是如此，我们必须小心应付，否则一个不好，就要吃大亏。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郎奉",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "一切安排妥当，尚书请放心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "郎奉",
      "listener": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "text": "尚书大人请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 142,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    }
  ],
